      *
     E                    FDLN       20 10               DSPFLD､LEN
     E                    AR30       30  1               DPSLAY
     E                    NLF        30 10               NEWLINE FLD
     E                    CHN        30  1 0             COLHDG NUM
     E                    SRC        80  1               SOURCE
     E                    EDTL    1   1  9               EDTCDE(L)
      *
     IINPUT   NS  79
     I                                        1   6 DSSEQ
     I                                        7  12 DSDAT
     I                                       13  17 DSMRK
